{"tid":1678891,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如果你認為會成立獨立調查會，就証明你係一個on9","createTime":"2019-10-28T01:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T04:00:54.000Z","uid":57125,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a988a8b72f8197d6ffd945dca6873f416adc1593","tid":1678891,"uid":57125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T01:29:50.000Z","msg":"係土共管治下，土共可以答應你換特首，俾你雙普選，俾埋錢你都得!但成立獨立調查會就一定唔得，事因係土共既管治模式一定要揸住枝槍，絕對唔可以俾枝槍指住自己，而香港有槍既一定係警察，現在既警隊已經唔係由肥仔聰去管，佢個人一早已經俾人架空左，呢家只得林鄭同中央可以管理，可能你會問香港唔係有老解咩！我可以話你知，老解只會暗地出，你睇下最近話叫返班老鬼返黎做已經係笑話，果班退休老鬼，退左之後自己都有正職，又唔跑得，唔通重同你上前駁火咩！返屋企同個孫玩唔好?跟本就係想正式溝班老解入警隊!<br />\n所以我認為，解散警隊係必定既事!成立獨立調查會已經係次要既事!"},{"pid":"731305bbb4de8af43e53e298b537920f6efdb323","tid":1678891,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T01:30:07.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcdd7c0745b125c6bdafedc90b100523531d5159","tid":1678891,"uid":57125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"731305bbb4de8af43e53e298b537920f6efdb323","tid":1678891,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T01:30:07.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T01:30:41.000Z","msg":"有d唔太update"},{"pid":"b0199c2de0c59eee5d4e51feb4a4b7a2278f09bb","tid":1678891,"uid":138427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T01:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ea05fbc638de9cc5663edcbb31b4c9c04b819d","tid":1678891,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T01:33:19.000Z","ms